long_description: Taking your four-legged friend on a hike and need a doggie meal for the trail? Bring the PowerBark Dog Food Bar. It's wholesome, natural and convenient. 100% complete and balanced meal in a portable 4 oz. bar. One PowerBark bar will feed a 30-pound adult dog adequately for one meal; if you feed your dog once a day, then you'll need to give your dog 2 bars at that feeding. PowerBark Dog Food Bars are vegetarian with added vitamins and minerals, and are free of wheat, corn, and preservatives. Provides your adult dog 100% of the protein a dog needs on a daily basis; the main source of protein is pea protein.
